Package io.github.zero88.schedulerx

Interface JobExecutorConfig<IN,OUT>

Type Parameters:
IN - Type of job input data
OUT - Type of job result data
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractScheduler, AbstractSchedulerBuilder
@Internal public interface JobExecutorConfig<IN,OUT>
Shared immutable fields between JobExecutor and its builder.

This class is designed to internal usage, don't refer it in your code.
